<em>Published in final edited form as: </em>Stat Med. 2018 Nov 28;38(9):1543–1557. doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/sim.8055" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10.1002/sim.8055</a>
</div>
