<li id="R3">
<span class="label">3.</span><cite>Taanila A, Murray GK, Jokelainen J, Isohanni M, Rantakallio P. Infant developmental milestones: a 31-year follow-up. Dev Med Child Neurol. 2005;47(9):581–586. 10.1111/j.1469-8749.2005.tb01207.x</cite> [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1469-8749.2005.tb01207.x" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI</a>] [<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16138663/" class="usa-link">PubMed</a>] [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Dev%20Med%20Child%20Neurol&amp;title=Infant%20developmental%20milestones:%20a%2031-year%20follow-up&amp;author=A%20Taanila&amp;author=GK%20Murray&amp;author=J%20Jokelainen&amp;author=M%20Isohanni&amp;author=P%20Rantakallio&amp;volume=47&amp;issue=9&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;pages=581-586&amp;pmid=16138663&amp;doi=10.1111/j.1469-8749.2005.tb01207.x&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
<li id="R4">
<span class="label">4.</span><cite>Benjamin Neelon SE, Oken E, Taveras EM, Rifas-Shiman SL, Gillman MW. Age of achievement of gross motor milestones in infancy and adiposity at age 3 years. Matern Child Health J. 2012;16(5):1015–1020. 10.1007/s10995-011-0828-3</cite> [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s10995-011-0828-3" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI</a>] [<a href="/articles/PMC3321389/" class="usa-link">PMC free article</a>] [<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21643834/" class="usa-link">PubMed</a>] [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Matern%20Child%20Health%20J&amp;title=Age%20of%20achievement%20of%20gross%20motor%20milestones%20in%20infancy%20and%20adiposity%20at%20age%203%20years&amp;author=SE%20Benjamin%20Neelon&amp;author=E%20Oken&amp;author=EM%20Taveras&amp;author=SL%20Rifas-Shiman&amp;author=MW%20Gillman&amp;volume=16&amp;issue=5&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;pages=1015-1020&amp;pmid=21643834&amp;doi=10.1007/s10995-011-0828-3&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
<li id="R5">
